A N A C T
RELATING TO PUBLIC UTILITIES AND CARRIERS -- LONG TERM CONTRACTING
STANDARDS FOR RENEWABLE ENERGY
Introduced By: Senators Tikoian, Lawson, Dimitri, Burke, Urso, Britto, Sosnowski,
Rogers, LaMountain, and de la Cruz
